{"tid":994284,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)皇家特工1-2 剋．寡婦","createTime":"2019-01-24T14:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T17:24:31.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a0c6ef6c9485cde740ae4c311c6bfcb4fa1f0a01","tid":994284,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T14:37:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=dtASCCMpoeTeRctmJjOlvQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=38001a4d\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=dtASCCMpoeTeRctmJjOlvQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=ae3f57d4\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=dtASCCMpoeTeRctmJjOlvQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c3044c49\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/8b/Kingsman_The_Secret_Service_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F8b%2FKingsman_The_Secret_Service_poster.jpg&h=fd1bb461&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/4/42/Kingsman_The_Golden_Circle_Poster.jpg/220px-Kingsman_The_Golden_Circle_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F4%2F42%2FKingsman_The_Golden_Circle_Poster.jpg%2F220px-Kingsman_The_Golden_Circle_Poster.jpg&h=3adf5e66&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.truemovie.com/2017Poster/widows_xlg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.truemovie.com%2F2017Poster%2Fwidows_xlg.jpg&h=e24b9dad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.「金士曼」表面上是英國倫敦薩佛街上的一家裁縫店，天天為客戶量身打造帥氣的西服，實際上卻是一個歷史淵源久遠的民間諜報組織，以世界和平為宗旨，曾經多次打擊了嚴重犯罪，卻極為低調，不欲人知。但他們的能力卻不亞於英國秘密情報局（俗稱軍情六處，MI6）、美國中央情報局（CIA）、俄國對外情報局（FIS，原為KGB第一總局）、以色列情報特務局（MOSSAD）等知名的國家情治單位，<br />\n1997年「金士曼」的一群探員潛入位於中東的恐怖組織巢穴，順利逮捕其首腦，特務哈利&middot;哈特（代號加拉哈德，取自英國傳奇《圓桌武士》）審問首腦時，卻因一時失誤沒發現首腦想用手榴彈同歸於盡，導致一名探員用肉身阻擋而英勇犧牲，雖然救了其他人，但也讓哈特感到十分愧疚......<br />\n<br />\n2.一年前，伊格西&middot;安文率間諜組織「金士曼特務」挫敗里奇蒙&middot;范倫坦播送神經波廣播毀滅全人類的陰謀後，拿下師父哈利&middot;哈特的代號－「加拉哈德」，和瑞典皇室的提兒蒂公主在一起生活。一次回家路上，在瓦倫丁事件中丟掉手臂和聲帶的金士曼特務落選者查理&middot;赫斯基伏擊了伊格西。伊格西在倫敦的飆車大戰中躲避查理與他一眾手下的追殺，但查理切斷他的機械手臂，利用車子的電腦系統駭入金士曼的伺服器。伊格西出席瑞典皇室晚宴期間，金士曼的總部和所有特務（除了梅林外）的住宅都被飛彈摧毀，英國所有金士曼特務都被除掉<br />\n<br />\n3.沉淪腐敗的芝加哥大街小巷裡，四名喪心病狂悍匪被殺身亡，死後遺下各自孤妻一筆爛帳，令她們身陷絕境。這四個生命毫無交集的寡婦，只好團結憑雙手以寡擊眾；拿回人生主導權，打造一個自己能夠主宰的未來。<br />\n<br />\n10 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=dtASCCMpoeTeRctmJjOlvQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=ddd15741\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=dtASCCMpoeTeRctmJjOlvQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=6be82dfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9423d8edc3aae6660550465b81cbbd303898af68","tid":994284,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T14:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07ce23497e03761bde0b4d5bf7e92be2311bb31","tid":994284,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e18879778e722f58f55a32ec53d851fe738966","tid":994284,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T16:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49acc5e5989bfdaf9b958e30f886330a480ce01","tid":994284,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T17:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}